songs.title: Impossible [Spanglish] (Cover)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Normani & Camila]
I remember years ago someone told me I should take
Caution when it comes to love, I did, I did
Y tú eras fuerte y yo no, mi error, mi ilusión
Sin cuidado, me olvidé, I did

[Pre-Chorus: Lauren]
Ahora
Ya esta hecho, no hay qué decir
Te marchaste y fue tan fácil
Has ganado, ya puedes contarles

[Chorus: Lauren & Ally & All]
Tell them all I know now, shout it from the roof top
Write it on the skyline, all we have is gone now
Dile que era feliz, mi corazón roto
All my scars are open, tell them what I hoped would be
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible

[Pre-Chorus: Dinah]
And now when all is gone, there is nothing to say
And if you're done with embarrassing me
On your own you can
Go ahead and tell them

[Chorus: Dinah & All]
Tell them all I know now, shout it from the roof top
Write it on the skyline, tell them what I hoped would be
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible

[Bridge: Camila]
I remember years ago, someone told me I should take
Caution when it comes to love, I did

[Chorus: Camila & Ally & All]
So tell them all I know now, shout it from the roof top
Write it on the skyline, all we had is gone now, oh
Tell them I was happy and my heart is broken
All my scars are open, tell them what I hoped would be
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
